[
  {
    "startTime": 4.459,
    "endTime": 5.526,
    "text": "Wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.7,
    "endTime": 10.263,
    "text": "I should warn you. Before you step inside the house, this could change the course of your entire life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.263,
    "endTime": 12.054,
    "text": "I'm not afraid of a couple ghosts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 15.927,
    "text": "Heh, you say that now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.3,
    "endTime": 28.466,
    "text": "This mansion is unhinged!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.7,
    "endTime": 32.755,
    "text": "These ghosts definitely don't want to leave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.4,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "Death lurks around every corner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.4,
    "endTime": 41.042,
    "text": "God, give us a break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.042,
    "endTime": 44.459,
    "text": "There's so many bad people in the world, haunt them!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.459,
    "endTime": 46.5,
    "text": "Amen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.8,
    "endTime": 48.8,
    "text": "I do like surprises."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 50.125,
    "text": "Is anybody else seeing this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.3,
    "endTime": 52.125,
    "text": "I hope you do too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.3,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.5,
    "endTime": 57.3,
    "text": "We're in a fight, whether we like it or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.478,
    "endTime": 60.5,
    "text": "Or else we're stuck here for eternity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.5,
    "endTime": 61.4,
    "text": "Gabbie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.597,
    "endTime": 70.3,
    "text": "If this comes down to an exorcism, we're in big trouble."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.5,
    "endTime": 73.334,
    "text": "This house is dripping with souls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.5,
    "endTime": 78.125,
    "text": "But there's always room..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.125,
    "endTime": 85.626,
    "text": "...for one more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.4,
    "endTime": 88.35300000000001,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 101.8,
    "text": "My friend was mugged."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.1,
    "endTime": 108.032,
    "text": "He was tall. He had hair that was sticking out of a top hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.032,
    "endTime": 109.25,
    "text": "Top hat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.25,
    "endTime": 110.8,
    "text": "Yes. Yeah, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.8,
    "endTime": 111.5,
    "text": "So, like, a top hat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.7,
    "endTime": 113.5,
    "text": "You would pull a rabbit out of it, probably."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.7,
    "endTime": 114.8,
    "text": "Uh, eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.9,
    "endTime": 116.126,
    "text": "There were a bit, uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.5,
    "endTime": 118.914,
    "text": "- Deep, sunken eyes. Beady eyes. - Like a raccoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.914,
    "endTime": 120.121,
    "text": "They were set back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.4,
    "endTime": 124.7,
    "text": "And... he was smiling, like... Yeah, like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.7,
    "endTime": 126.25,
    "text": "- This kind of thing. - Exactly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.25,
    "endTime": 128.083,
    "text": "Is this the man who mugged you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.083,
    "endTime": 129.167,
    "text": "- Wow! - Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.167,
    "endTime": 131.751,
    "text": "You just did that, just now?"
  }
]